*
         * @prop {String} userType
         * @description
         *   The type for the current output, allowed values are 'system', 'agent' and 'customer'.

*
         * @prop {String|undefined} realname
         * @description
         *   The given realname will be used to build the initials as a fallback.

*
         * @computed {String} initials
         * @description
         *   Return the user initials based on the user name.
